text.section:
The Department shall adopt regulations that include:
Minimum qualifications to obtain a waterfowl outfitter and waterfowl hunting guide license and other application requirements;
Procedures for the review of applications;
Criteria for the issuance and denial of licenses;
Grounds for license suspension and revocation;
Standards for the conduct of waterfowl outfitters and waterfowl hunting guides; and
Any other provisions the Department finds necessary to regulate waterfowl outfitters and waterfowl hunting guides.
